english: The weather is beautiful today.
spanish: El clima está hermoso hoy.

english: She reads books every evening.
spanish: Ella lee libros todas las noches.

english: The children play in the park.
spanish: Los niños juegan en el parque.

english: We need to solve this problem.
spanish: Necesitamos resolver este problema.

english: The meeting starts at three o'clock.
spanish: La reunión comienza a las tres.

english: He works at a technology company.
spanish: Él trabaja en una empresa de tecnología.

english: The restaurant serves excellent food.
spanish: El restaurante sirve comida excelente.

english: They travel to different countries.
spanish: Ellos viajan a diferentes países.

english: The teacher explains the lesson clearly.
spanish: El profesor explica la lección claramente.

english: We celebrate birthdays with cake.
spanish: Celebramos los cumpleaños con pastel.

english: The dog runs through the garden.
spanish: El perro corre por el jardín.

english: She studies medicine at university.
spanish: Ella estudia medicina en la universidad.

english: The movie was very interesting.
spanish: La película fue muy interesante.

english: They built a new house last year.
spanish: Construyeron una casa nueva el año pasado.

english: The coffee tastes better with sugar.
spanish: El café sabe mejor con azúcar.

english: We walk along the beach every morning.
spanish: Caminamos por la playa cada mañana.

english: The library has thousands of books.
spanish: La biblioteca tiene miles de libros.

english: He plays guitar in a band.
spanish: Él toca guitarra en una banda.

english: The train arrives at noon.
spanish: El tren llega al mediodía.

english: She writes articles for newspapers.
spanish: Ella escribe artículos para periódicos.

english: The city lights shine at night.
spanish: Las luces de la ciudad brillan por la noche.

english: We need more time to finish.
spanish: Necesitamos más tiempo para terminar.

english: The flowers bloom in spring.
spanish: Las flores florecen en primavera.

english: He teaches mathematics to students.
spanish: Él enseña matemáticas a los estudiantes.

english: The computer needs a software update.
spanish: La computadora necesita una actualización de software.

english: They dance at the festival.
spanish: Ellos bailan en el festival.

english: The museum displays ancient artifacts.
spanish: El museo exhibe artefactos antiguos.

english: We cook dinner together every Sunday.
spanish: Cocinamos la cena juntos cada domingo.

english: The birds sing in the morning.
spanish: Los pájaros cantan por la mañana.

english: She paints beautiful landscapes.
spanish: Ella pinta hermosos paisajes.

english: The store opens at eight o'clock.
spanish: La tienda abre a las ocho.

english: They study languages at school.
spanish: Ellos estudian idiomas en la escuela.

english: The river flows through the valley.
spanish: El río fluye por el valle.

english: We watch movies on weekends.
spanish: Vemos películas los fines de semana.

english: The scientist conducts important research.
spanish: El científico realiza investigaciones importantes.
